    <h2>Major in Creative Technologies</h2>
    </div>

    <p class="specialp">The <span class="spanreal"> interdisciplinary Creative Technologie major </span>emphasizes design and practice in the integration of digital technologies and the fine arts. In addition to foundational study across the fine arts, the major provides training and experiences across a range of creative/technical fields including video, sound, electronic music, music production, gaming, motion graphics, interactivity, AR/VR, UI/UX, mobile, web, and computer programming concepts.</p>
